r who brings to harvard an extraordinary breadth of experience in research across disciplines fsi director coit d blacker the olivier nomellini professor in international studies said we congratulate alan on his appointment as provost of harvard we will miss his probing intellect his contributions to scholarship and public policy and his keen appreciation of the challenges facing research universities in a message to colleagues alan garber said my time on the faculty at stanford has been wonderful in every important way the past 13 years when chp and pcor were created and grew have been the high point of my stanford career stanford report harvard names stanford medical school professor alan m garber as its next provost harvard gazette alan garber named provost search chp search within everything courses events fellowships news op eds people publications research other pages news of interest population reference bureau interviews alan garber may 20 2011 news in new england journal commentary shp director alan garber explores the role of fda in regulating devices march 24 2010 announcement director alan garber discusses comparative effectiveness research at brookings event december 2 2009 announcement alan garber receives career achievement award from society for medical decision making november 11 2009 news director alan garber discusses patient care in nyt magazine article making health care better in the news new york times on november 8 2009 alan garber discusses tiered co payment findings in wall street journal article december 5 2003 in the news support map & directions contact rss+ rss xml feeds freeman spogli institute for international studies encina hall 616 serra st stanford ca 94305 6055 tel 650 736 0815 fax 650 725 2592 mail code 6055
